*Bolestan* sam od prehlade. (I am sick with a cold.)
On je *bolestan* i neće biti u školi. (He is sick and won't be in school.)
Moj sin je nedavno bio *bolestan*. (My son was recently ill.)
Njen otac je bio veoma *bolestan*. (Her father was very ill.)
Ona je bila *bolestan* od prehlade nekoliko dana. (She was sick with a cold for a few days.)
Moj deda je bio *bolestan* i morao je da odlazi na bolničko lečenje. (My grandfather was ill and had to go to hospital for treatment.)